{
  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed outbuilding would, as a result of the inclusion of primary living accommodation in the form of a basic kitchen facility and shower room, raise the risk of facilitating uses which would be non-incidental to the main house and which would harm neighbouring living conditions, contrary to Local Plan policies CC2 and SC7 and the intent of the Residential Extension Guidelines.",
    "Reason : 2 - The proposed outbuilding, due to its excessive size and scale and non-incidental use would, when considered in conjunction with the existing extensions at the site, result in a disproportionate form of development and an overdevelopment of the site. As a result, the proposal would have a negative impact on the character and appearance of the area, contrary to Local Plan policies CC1 and SC7 and the intent of the Residential Extension Guidelines."
